# Server backend

Entry: `server.ts` → `dist/server.cjs`

## Модули (server/)

| Файл | Назначение |
|------|------------|
| dataStore.ts | load/save, revision, JSON/SQL |
| purgeWorkspace.ts | empty inventory payload (keep users/license) |
| apiAuth.ts | requireAuth, requireAdminRole, license write gate |
| sessionEngine.ts | sessions, heartbeat, revoke |
| userCredentials.ts | setup, password hash, seed via `defaultWorkspaceSeed.ts` |
| licenseCore.ts | server license snapshot |
| updateEngine.ts | GitHub update check/apply |

## API (основное)

| Method | Path | Auth | Назначение |
|--------|------|------|------------|
| GET | `/api/health` | — | version |
| GET/POST | `/api/auth/setup-status`, `/setup` | — | first run |
| POST | `/api/auth/authenticate` | — | login |
| GET/POST | `/api/data` | session | workspace CRUD + revision |
| POST | `/api/data/purge-workspace` | Admin | полная очистка инвентаризации |
| GET/POST | `/api/backup/export\|import` | Admin | backup |
| GET/POST | `/api/update/check\|apply` | Admin | auto-update |

## Env

`PORT` · `DB_ENCRYPTION_KEY` · `STACK_DATA_DIR` · `SKIP_OBFUSCATION`

## Build

`npm run build` = Vite client + esbuild server

При изменении API — синхронно: `apiClient.ts`, `workspaceSync.ts`, `sessionAuth.ts`.
